title: Elf wo Karu Mono-tachi Returns
original_name: エルフを狩るモノたちリターンズ
sinopse: Soon Celcia's 15-years-in-office-annivisary is to be held, and Ritsuko wants to participate. But from her idea of going peacefully into the world of the Elves, a sudden invasion from the Elven world into Jinboumachi, Tokyo begins.
